Class ComponentManager.Component

  • java.lang.Object
    • cinnamon.engine.system.ComponentManager.Component
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public abstract static class ComponentManager.Component
extends Object
implements Identifiable, Copier<ComponentManager.Component>

    Base class for all game object components to attach to a game object.

      • attach

        public final void attach(GameObjectManager.GObject host)

        Attaches to a host.

        If the given Identifiable has the same id and version as the Component's current host, this method does nothing.

        If the Component is currently attached to another Identifiable, added OnDetachListeners are notified before the new id and version are adopted and OnAttachListeners are called.

        Parameters:
        host - id and version to adopt.

      • clear

        public final void clear()

        Resets all values and removes all OnAttachListeners and OnDetachListeners.

      • copy

        public final void copy(ComponentManager.Component object)

        Copies properties of the given component.

        This method should only be used to copy like components (e.g. a BodyComponent can only copy another BodyComponent). The following are exempt from copying:

        • OnAttachListeners
        • OnDetachListeners
        • Game object id and version
        Specified by:
        copy in interface Copier<ComponentManager.Component>
        Parameters:
        object - to copy.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if the given component type's class does not match.

      • detach

        public final void detach()

        Detaches from a host.

        If the Component is not currently attached to anything, this method does nothing. Otherwise, added OnDetachListeners are notified.
